These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, subway, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Transport        | scooter | helicopter   | bike | subway    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, orchid, dahlia
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsdaisy is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Flower   | dahlia    | daisy | orchid | poppy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, july, december
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday          | december | july | october    | february      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, dahlia, marigold
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsmarigold##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Flower   | dahlia       | bellflower   | zinnia    | marigold  |

