.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, freelancer, nurse
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the freelancer is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the nurse##1
3. the indian is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the manager is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Job   | manager  | photographer    | freelancer   | nurse       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

