3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Food   | blueberry | peach     | strawberry  | kale  |

