.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, tiparillo, fonseca
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
2. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the swisher-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the alhambra-smoker##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the swisher-smoker and the owner of the goat##2
8. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Cigar   | alhambra | swisher      | fonseca | tiparillo |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

