.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, brazilian, thai, colombian
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, turtle
1. the thai is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the egyptian is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the thai##2
4. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
5. the thai is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian   | egyptian | thai |
| Pet    | turtle     | hamster | cat     | mouse  |

