.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, documentary, crime, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the person watching sports movies is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the person watching crime movies##2
4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary       | crime   | sports | epic |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

