.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, dancer, police-officer, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, firefighter-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is firefighter-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is firefighter-polo is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the dancer is on the left or right of the police-officer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | lawyer   | firefighter   | dancer      | police-officer      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | firefighter-polo | biathlon |

