.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, indian, nigerian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the chinese is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the indian##2
2. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the japanese is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Nationality   | japanese | indian         | chinese   | nigerian |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

