.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee | 7up    | fanta |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

