.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, juice, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the helicopter##2
4. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | juice   | 7up | milk |
| Transport   | van          | jet-ski | helicopter         | subway  |

 